Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and grammar analysis. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses probabilistic comparison algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with automated assessment of student's answers. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses the reduction of the problem to numerical solution of systems of equations. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the application of the approach to automatic assessment of student's answers in computer science.
